<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TT2.6">
<l>vāḷaik kiḷara vaḷaivā ḷeyiṟṟu vaṇṇac ciṟukūkai</l>
<l>mūḷait talaiyum piṇamum viḻuṅki muralu mutukāṭṭiṟ</l>
<l>ṟāḷip paṉaiyi ṉilaipōl mayirkkaṭ ṭaḻalvā yaḻalkaṭpēy</l>
<l>kūḷik kaṇaṅkaḷ kuḻalō ṭiyampak kuḻaka ṉāṭumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>On the old cremation ground, where colourful little owls with teeth curved [and]</l>
<l>shining so as to surpass a sword, devours skulls with brain [and] corpses [and] call,</l>
<l>while demonesses – fire mouths, fire eyes, hair tied like leaves of Palmyra trees –</l>
<l>[and] groups of demons make flute music, the Young one is dancing.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
